{
  "uid": "invos-analytics",
  "title": "invos · Invoice Analytics",
  "description": "Live view of ingested invoices (PostgreSQL). Totals and the commodity-type breakdown count the whole table; the time charts use created_at (ingest time). Start with an empty DB and run a test to watch it fill.",
  "tags": ["invos", "business", "postgres"],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 2,
  "editable": true,
  "time": { "from": "now-15m", "to": "now" },
  "refresh": "5s",
  "timezone": "utc",
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Total invoices",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": null } ] } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "value", "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT count(*) AS \"total invoices\" FROM invoices"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Total line items",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "steps": [ { "color": "blue", "value": null } ] } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "value", "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT count(*) AS \"total line items\" FROM invoice_items"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Total revenue (NTD)",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "currencyNTD", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "steps": [ { "color": "purple", "value": null } ] } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "value", "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT COALESCE(sum(total_amount), 0) AS \"total revenue\" FROM invoices"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Invoices ingested per 5s (by ingest time)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "custom": { "drawStyle": "bars", "fillOpacity": 40 } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "single" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
          "format": "time_series",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT $__timeGroupAlias(created_at, '5s'), count(*) AS \"invoices ingested\" FROM invoices WHERE $__timeFilter(created_at) GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Invoices in DB (cumulative)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2 } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "single" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
          "format": "time_series",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT time, sum(c) OVER (ORDER BY time) AS \"invoices (cumulative)\" FROM (SELECT $__timeGroup(created_at, '5s') AS time, count(*) AS c FROM invoices WHERE $__timeFilter(created_at) GROUP BY 1) t ORDER BY time"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Line items by commodity type",
      "type": "barchart",
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 13 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "xField": "category", "orientation": "horizontal", "showValue": "auto", "legend": { "showLegend": false } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "postgres" },
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT it.category AS \"category\", count(*) AS \"line items\" FROM invoice_items it GROUP BY it.category ORDER BY \"line items\" DESC"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 13 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### What to look for\n\nStart from an **empty database** (`bash scripts/run.sh up` does not replay), then run a test (`bash scripts/run.sh smoke`).\n\n- **Total invoices / line items / revenue** tick up live as invoices arrive.\n- **Invoices ingested per 5s** and **cumulative** show the database filling from zero, by ingest time (`created_at`).\n- **Line items by commodity type** shows the generic commodity mix growing.\n\nInvoices are dated on the fly at emit time, so everything you see is happening _now_. Auto-refresh is 5s."
      }
    }
  ]
}
